com.lody.welike.http.callback

类 HttpCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lody.welike.http.callback.HttpCallback
  • 直接已知子类:
    FileUploadCallback, HttpBitmapCallback, HttpResultCallback

    public abstract class HttpCallback
extends java.lang.Object
    Http请求的回调基础回调, 你只需要复写你需要回调的那部分方法. 上传文件时可以使用FileUploadCallback.
    作者:
    lody
